name: Indraprasth Food
overview:
We Indraprasth Foods Ltd a Unit Of Shri Hiralal Chironjilal Agrawal Since 1962 are exporter, importer and supplier of Agro Products like Chick Peas, Soybean, Wheat, Maize, Gram, Sesame Seed, Mustard Seed like Black Mustard Seeds, Yellow Mustard Seeds, Ground Nut, and Cumin Seeds.

Products: Maize, Gram, Sesame Seed, Mustard Seed like Black Mustard Seeds, Yellow Mustard Seeds, Ground Nut, and Cumin Seeds.

Our Team:
Our team comprises highly qualified and talented professionals, who have in-depth understanding in this domain. We have appointed these professionals after analyzing them on aspects like educational qualification, experience and industry knowledge.

Our Quality Assurance:
Our widespread network allows us to connect with most-quality centric manufacturers of the market. This helps us in bringing forth most qualitative range of products in various grades and specifications.

Research and Development:
It is important for every organization to completely understand the changing market trends and be at par with them. In order to achieve this, we have established a well-equipped R&D unit at our premises, which is looked after by our R&D professionals in an effective manner, who are well-versed in this line of work.
